<style>
  .verification-button-container {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }

  .verification-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white !important;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .verification-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white !important;
  }

  .verification-link {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 12px;
    font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    word-break: break-all;
    color: #6c757d;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .code-expiry {
    color: #6c757d;
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .alert {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .alert-info {
    background-color: #e3f2fd;
    border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
  }

  .security-info {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }

  .security-info-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #495057;
  }

  .security-info-content {
    color: #6c757d;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>

<p>Welcome to CareerBridge AI! We're excited to have you join our community as a
  <strong>{{roleDisplayName}}</strong>.</p>

<p>To complete your account setup and start exploring opportunities, please
  verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>

<div class='verification-button-container'>
  <a
    href='{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email?token={{verificationToken}}&email={{email}}'
    class='verification-button'
  >
    Verify Email Address
  </a>
  <div class='code-expiry'>This link expires in 24 hours</div>
</div>

<p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your
  browser:</p>
<div class='verification-link'>
  {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email?token={{verificationToken}}&email={{email}}
</div>

<div class='alert alert-info'>
  <strong>What's Next?</strong><br />
  After verification, you'll have access to:
  <ul>
    {{#each features}}
      <li>{{this}}</li>
    {{/each}}
  </ul>
</div>

<div class='security-info'>
  <div class='security-info-title'>ðŸ”’ Security Notice</div>
  <div class='security-info-content'>
    If you didn't create an account with CareerBridge AI, please ignore this
    email. Your security is our priority. This verification link can only be
    used once.
  </div>
</div>

<p>Need help? Our support team is here to assist you every step of the way.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br />
  <strong>The CareerBridge AI Team</strong></p>